ET
BT
/F1 10 Tf
72.0 332.0 Td
(the specific content, but the shape of the approach. The buildup is unmistakable. Your) Tj
ET
BT
/F1 10 Tf
72.0 318.0 Td
(attention has narrowed, your breathing has slowed slightly, and you are tracking) Tj
ET
BT
/F1 10 Tf
72.0 304.0 Td
(everything the performer is doing with a kind of focused pleasure that is slightly) Tj
ET
BT
/F1 10 Tf
72.0 290.0 Td
(uncomfortable. The impossible moment, when it arrives, is not a surprise exactly. It is a) Tj
ET
BT
/F1 10 Tf
72.0 276.0 Td
(fulfillment. But of what? Of a prediction you were building toward without knowing its) Tj
ET
BT
/F1 10 Tf
72.0 262.0 Td
(destination. That structure ? the confident build toward an unresolvable outcome ? is the) Tj
ET
