ET
BT
/F1 10 Tf
72.0 648.0 Td
(at a cold outdoor show is thermoregulation. Arms crossed during a one-on-one reading is a) Tj
ET
BT
/F1 10 Tf
72.0 634.0 Td
(barrier. Context determines meaning. Always.) Tj
ET
BT
/F1 10 Tf
72.0 612.0 Td
