ET
BT
/F1 10 Tf
72.0 512.0 Td
(generic chart. Deviation from their baseline is the data point. Baseline is the key.) Tj
ET
BT
/F1 10 Tf
72.0 498.0 Td
(Without it, every read is a projection.) Tj
ET
BT
/F1 10 Tf
72.0 476.0 Td
(Culture. Factor in the norms of the person's background. Many behaviors are culturally) Tj
ET
BT
/F1 10 Tf
72.0 462.0 Td
(specific. Eye contact norms, personal space, and emotional expressiveness vary) Tj
ET
BT
/F1 10 Tf
72.0 448.0 Td
(significantly. Calibrate before concluding.) Tj
ET
